        "Description": "Eep! WH-WHAT WAS THAT!?\r\nDon\u0027t sneak up on me, Hunter!\r\nI-I\u0027ve been on edge ever since\r\na Zinogre j-jumped out on me!\r\nBrr...my fur\u0027s still on end from\r\nthe fear...a-and static! Could\r\ny-you help me-me-meow-t?",
